---
// src/pages/zh/index.astro
// ==========================================
// VETERAN.CORE // CHINESE HOMEPAGE
// ==========================================
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>VETERAN.CORE // 22年硬件行家与BOM元器件代换优化</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style is:inline>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #09090b !important;
        color: #fafafa !important;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      
      .gveh-header { 
        padding: 30px 5%; 
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.3);
        display: flex !important;
        justify-content: space-between !important;
        align-items: center !important;
      }
      .gveh-logo { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important; color: #f59e0b !important; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
      
      .gveh-lang-top-btn {
        text-decoration: none !important;
        font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important;
        font-size: 12px !important;
        font-weight: 700 !important;
        color: #fafafa !important;
        border: 1px solid rgba(161, 161, 170, 0.4) !important;
        padding: 6px 14px !important;
        border-radius: 4px !important;
        background: rgba(24, 24, 27, 0.5) !important;
        transition: all 0.3s ease !important;
      }
      .gveh-lang-top-btn:hover {
        color: #f59e0b !important;
        border-color: #f59e0b !important;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2) !important;
      }

      .gveh-hero { max-width: 1200px; margin: 100px auto 60px auto; padding: 0 40px; text-align: center; }
      .gveh-hero h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #ffffff; }
      .gveh-hero h1 span { color: #f59e0b !important; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important; }
      .gveh-hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #a1a1aa !important; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; }
      
      .gveh-matrix { max-width: 1200px; margin: 40px auto 180px auto; padding: 0 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
      .gveh-card { background-color: #141417 !important; border: 1px solid rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.4) !important; padding: 32px; border-radius: 4px; }
      .gveh-card-tag { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important; color: #f59e0b !important; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .gveh-card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #ffffff; }
      .gveh-card p { color: #a1a1aa !important; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .gveh-hero { margin: 60px auto 30px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .gveh-hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
        .gveh-matrix { grid-template-columns: 1fr; margin-bottom: 140px; padding: 0 20px; }
      }

      /* 📡 智能悬浮舱呼吸动效逻辑 */
      .gveh-nav-container {
        position: fixed !important; bottom: 0 !important; left: 50% !important; transform: translateX(-50%) !important;
        padding-bottom: 28px !important; padding-top: 50px !important; z-index: 999999 !important;
        display: flex !important; justify-content: center !important; align-items: center !important; cursor: pointer !important;
      }
      .gveh-hover-pill {
        border: 1px solid rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.2) !important; padding: 8px 24px !important;
        display: flex !important; justify-content: center !important; align-items: center !important; gap: 36px !important; border-radius: 9999px !important;
        opacity: 0.15 !important; transform: translateY(15px) scale(0.98) !important;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) !important;
        background-color: rgba(20, 20, 23, 0.4) !important; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-container:hover .gveh-hover-pill {
        opacity: 1 !important; transform: translateY(0) scale(1) !important;
        background-color: rgba(24, 24, 27, 0.98) !important;
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px) !important; -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) !important;
        border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4) !important;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.7), 0 0 20px rgba(245,158,11,0.15) !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-item {
        text-decoration: none !important; display: flex !important; flex-direction: column !important;
        align-items: center !important; gap: 3px !important; color: rgba(161, 161, 170, 0.7) !important; transition: all 0.2s ease !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-text {
        font-size: 10px !important; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0.1em !important;
        text-transform: uppercase !important; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-item:hover { color: #f59e0b !important; }
      .gveh-nav-item.active { color: #f59e0b !important; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <header class="gveh-header">
      <div class="gveh-logo">// VETERAN.CORE //</div>
      <a href="/" class="gveh-lang-top-btn">中文 / EN</a>
    </header>

    <main style="flex: 1;">
      <section class="gveh-hero">
        <h1>不要只是采购元器件。<br />用 <span>22 年</span> 硬件行业经验，帮您优化每一颗芯片。</h1>
        <p>[坐标: 深圳] // 为全球工程师提供独立分析、品质标准和战略元器件替代优化。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="gveh-matrix">
        <div class="gveh-card">
          <div class="gveh-card-tag">// MODULE_01</div>
          <h2>国产 vs 全球</h2>
          <p>深度可靠性测试、交叉参考分析，以及国产替代方案与一线品牌的真实对比。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gveh-card">
          <div class="gveh-card-tag">// MODULE_02</div>
          <h2>BOM 优化</h2>
          <p>不降低品质的成本降低策略。生命周期管理和供应链风险缓解指南。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gveh-card">
          <div class="gveh-card-tag">// MODULE_03</div>
          <h2>关于我</h2>
          <p>2004 年扎根深圳，22 年硬核硬件研发及市场经验，做您在元器件市场清澈透明的耳目。</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div class="gveh-nav-container">
      <div class="gveh-hover-pill">
        
        <a href="/zh" class="gveh-nav-item active">
          <svg style="width:18px; height:18px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
          <span class="gveh-nav-text">HOME</span>
        </a>
        
        <div style="width: 1px !important; height: 16px !important; background-color: rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.5) !important;"></div>

        <a href="/bom-hub" class="gveh-nav-item">
          <svg style="width:18px; height:18px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
          <span class="gveh-nav-text">BOM HUB</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>